<section class="relative w-full bg-white overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial-pink opacity-30" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="pt-16 sm:pt-20 lg:pt-24 pb-12 sm:pb-16 lg:pb-20">
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 sm:mb-14">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 mb-4 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-700">
         Limited Beta - 20 spots left
        </div>
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6" style="color: var(--neutral-900);">
          Stop Losing New Members After Their First Class
        </h1>
        
        <p class="font-body text-base sm:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-10" style="color: var(--neutral-600);">
Automated post-class follow-ups that, per FitGrid case studies, drive 87% more spend from first-timers—live in 5 minutes for $29/month, versus $299/month for FitGrid Retain.        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-6">
          <a href="#waitlist" class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-600 transition rounded-lg shadow-lg cursor-pointer" data-astro-interactive>
            Get Early Access — Save $270/mo
          </a>
          <a href="#calculator" class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold border border-rose-200 text-rose-600 bg-white hover:border-rose-300 transition rounded-lg cursor-pointer">
            See Real Results
          </a>
        </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-6">
            Transparent $29/month pricing—FitGrid Retain costs $299/month for comparable follow-up automation and member feedback collection.
          </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm text-neutral-600">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Mindbody Sync</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Cancel Anytime</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Instructor-Friendly</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-neutral-500">
         Pre-launch beta: we're onboarding 20 studios to shape the final product.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Interactive Calculator -->
